29
00:06:25,521 --> 00:06:26,951
From the gentleman.

30
00:06:26,951 --> 00:06:28,581
Where?

31
00:06:33,591 --> 00:06:35,591
Do you know him?

32
00:06:37,501 --> 00:06:38,741
Find out who he is.

33
00:06:38,741 --> 00:06:39,991
