67
00:09:19,161 --> 00:09:21,231
Martin?

68
00:09:21,231 --> 00:09:23,311
Yes, sir.

69
00:09:23,311 --> 00:09:25,121
Who is that man?

70
00:09:26,491 --> 00:09:28,591
That... That's Oskar Schindler!

71
00:10:37,431 --> 00:10:39,861
The Jewish Council

72
00:10:39,861 --> 00:10:42,831
